Trevor Sean White, a forensic auditor of accounting firm PriceWaterhouseCoopers, is testifying at the Zondo Commission today. JOHANNESBURG - Trevor Sean White, a forensic auditor of accounting firm PriceWaterhouseCoopers, is testifying at the Zondo Commission on Monday. His name came up last week during the testimony of retired Colonel Johannes van Loggerenberg. White's testimony is related to alleged criminal activities of Durban based businessman Thoshan Panday. PWC apparently vetted Panday.